casebody.data:
Ohio Holding Company, Appellant, v. City of Grove City, Appellee.

[Cite as Ohio Holding Co. v. Grove City (1991), 58 Ohio St. 3d 605.]

(No. 90-347 Submitted January 22, 1991 Decided February 27, 1991.) Lucas, Prendergast, Albright, Gibson & Newman and Rankin M. Gibson, for appellant. Brisker & Eckler, James A. Readey and Anne Marie Sferra, for appellee.

The appeal is dismissed, sua sponte, as having been improvidently allowed.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
